discovery_transcript:
{
  "messages": [
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Hi, thank you for taking the time to speak with me today. My name is Emily and I'm a sales representative from Whatfix. Can you please start by telling me a little bit about yourself and your role at Schneider Electric?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "Hi Emily, nice to meet you. My name is David and I'm the Head of Digital Adoption at Schneider Electric. I'm responsible for ensuring that our employees and customers are able to effectively use our energy management software to meet their sustainability goals."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "That's great, David. Can you tell me more about the challenges you're currently facing in terms of digital adoption and employee onboarding? How are you currently supporting your employees and customers in their use of your energy management software?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "One of our biggest challenges is ensuring that our employees are efficient in using our energy management systems. We've found that if they're not properly trained, they can waste a lot of time and resources, which ultimately affects our sustainability goals. We're currently using a lot of manual processes and guides, but we're finding that they're not very effective."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "I understand. It sounds like you're looking for a more efficient and effective way to support your employees in their use of your energy management software. Have you considered using a digital adoption platform like Whatfix to provide in-app guidance and support?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "Actually, that's what we're looking for. We want to find a solution that can provide personalized onboarding experiences for our employees and customers, as well as analytics capabilities to track user adoption. We've heard of Whatfix and were interested in learning more about your platform."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Great. Our digital adoption platform is designed to help organizations like yours improve user adoption of their software applications. Our platform provides a no-code editor to create in-app guidance and support, as well as analytics capabilities to track user behavior and adoption. We've had a lot of success with similar organizations in the energy management space."
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "That sounds very interesting. Can you tell me more about how Whatfix's platform can support our sustainability goals? We're looking for a solution that can help us reduce our carbon footprint and improve our overall efficiency."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Absolutely. Our platform is designed to help organizations reduce their carbon footprint by improving the efficiency of their energy management processes. We've found that by providing in-app guidance and support, organizations can reduce their energy consumption and improve their overall sustainability. We'd be happy to provide you with some case studies of similar organizations that have seen significant reductions in their carbon footprint after implementing our platform."
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "That would be great, thank you. I'm also interested in learning more about your pricing plans and how they can be customized to fit our specific needs. We're a large-scale business with diverse stakeholder needs, so we need a solution that can be tailored to our specific requirements."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Absolutely. We offer customized pricing plans for large-scale businesses like yours. We can work with you to develop a pricing plan that meets your specific needs and requirements. We also have a tiered pricing structure that allows you to scale up or down depending on your business needs."
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "That sounds very flexible. I'm also interested in learning more about your implementation process and how you support your customers during the onboarding process. We've had some bad experiences with other vendors in the past, so we want to make sure that we're working with a vendor that can provide us with top-notch support."
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "I completely understand. We take our customer support very seriously at Whatfix. We have a dedicated customer success team that works with our customers to ensure a smooth implementation and onboarding process. We also provide ongoing support and training to ensure that our customers are getting the most out of our platform."
    },
    {
      "user": "Schneider Electric",
      "content": "That sounds great. I think we're interested in moving forward with a proof of concept to see how Whatfix's platform can support our digital adoption goals. Can you walk me through the next steps and what we can expect during the proof of concept process?"
    },
    {
      "user": "Whatfix",
      "content": "Absolutely. I'd be happy to walk you through the next steps. We'll work with you to develop a customized proof of concept that meets your specific needs and requirements. During the proof of concept process, we'll provide you with access to our platform and work with your team to develop some customized guides and support. We'll also provide you with some analytics and reporting to help you track user adoption and behavioral data."
    }
  ]
}

